name: Eli Hoffman
text: This spot is worth giving a shot. They have big portions for convenient rates. Always well kept and with good atmosphere. Will come back again.

name: Sun Kings
text: Pizza was extremely greasy could barely hold it. Idk when pizza huts pizza got so greasy but NO THANKS. Also they don‚Äôt really toss your wings all the way. I‚Äôve never witnessed an establishment stingy with wing sauce lol wow. Below average for sure guess you get what you pay for

name: Candace Bates
text: We've never had bad pizza or service from this location. My only issue is the sauces we order and pay for are never delivered...never. I refuse to call over $0.60, but it's a bit aggravating that this continues to be the case. Still, you should enjoy the food and delivery service here!

name: Rick Vela
text: They're usually always very good, but sometimes they get skimpy with their toppings.

name: Kenneth Randall
text: The food and service were above our expectations. I really loved the environment of this place. Amazing restaurant to take my family out for dinner.

name: Jamar Salas
text: We like a lot to go out. Yesterday we  found this delicious restaurant which friends told us about. We enjoyed a beautiful evening there with very good cooking and a professional stuff and a distinguished chief cook. We  added this restaurant in our list  and we shall surely visit again very soon. We highly recommend.

name: Robert Thibeault
text: This spot is my favorite. I go to plenty of restaurants but to this restaurant I  constantly return again and again. The crew is very helpful and the cooking they serve is so fresh and tasty. I never miss an opportunity to have a nice dinner in this place. I highly recommend this place.

name: Brenda Saenz
text: Adam took my order and had fantastic customer service. Calling in the order is half of the transaction and he handled that part well. Kudos, thank you for being so pleasant!

name: Dianna Evans
text: Customer for over 10 yrs....wrong pizza delivered & it was cold.   Manager hung up on us....may have just lost a great customer whom tipped very well!! ‚Ä¶More

name: Horror Explained
text: Ordered lunch, never arrived. Called to find out they had cancelled my order with no notification. Manager had no explanation as to why. So they sent my order out, now over an hour late, to attempt to try to charge me for it again. Refused, they left with the pizza. Now my lunch period is over, no food and still no refund.
